INDICATIVE COST ESTIMATES
=========================
The pricing data embedded in this software (SaaS subscription costs, consultant
rates, sovereign installation tiers) reflects publicly visible UK market rates
at time of publication and is INDICATIVE ONLY. Actual quotes from consultants
and SaaS vendors vary by region, deal size, custom configuration, and
negotiation. The savings figures generated by this tool are estimates based on
the embedded rates; users should validate against actual quotes for their
specific situation before making purchasing decisions.

The authors accept no liability for procurement, contractual, or financial
decisions made on the basis of this software's output.
